description.content: Captain Jack is an unique mix between party music and millitary-dance-sound that brings everyone on the dancefloor. He's one of the most wellknown 90's eurodance acts worldwide - created 1995 by the german music producer Udo Niebergall. The uniform and the red hat are the trademarks of Captain Jack.
